    'Postscript ranks first for Shopify SMS marketing campaigns — VIP drop access, restrained broadcast cadence, and cart urgency tuned for DTC promo discipline. Noir Collective runs Thursday streetwear drops on Postscript VIP segments; SoleDrop ATX sells size runs in 11 minutes with waitlist-priority SMS.',
    'Not an email platform. Pair with Sequenzy for lifecycle email — welcome, education, winback belong in inbox. Campaign calendar collision is the failure mode when both channels fire identical offers within hours.',
    'Model BFCM SMS volume before scaling. Postscript wins when text is a primary campaign channel with segment-by-value governance, not a recovery afterthought.',
  ],
