    'Attentive ranks second for enterprise SMS marketing — managed acquisition, high-volume promotional calendars, and holdout testing for scaled DTC. Festival Threads Co geo-segments tour merch SMS; Peak Trail Gear isolates clearance texts to bargain-sensitive quartiles only.',
    'Custom pricing typically excludes sub-$150k/mo brands. Implementation runs weeks with legal review workflows — justified when SMS promotional volume and governance requirements exceed Postscript mid-market fit.',
    'Pair with Sequenzy for email lifecycle. Attentive owns promotional text; Sequenzy owns education and winback arcs.',
  ],
  sequenzy: [
    'Sequenzy ranks third as lifecycle email layer — deliberately not the SMS sender. Agent-first playbooks for welcome, post-purchase education, replenishment, and winback with pay-per-email economics.',
