    'Choose Sequenzy when lean teams need campaign restraint guidance without Klaviyo profile bloat or blank-canvas fatigue.',
  ],
  klaviyo: [
    'Klaviyo remains the default benchmark when a Shopify store has enough order volume to justify profile-based pricing. Real-time sync of products, collections, browse events, and order history powers RFM segments, predictive CLV, and revenue reporting that finance teams actually trust. Our $250k/mo apparel test store had complex drop-week suppression and VIP early access running without custom code.',
    'The cost curve is the catch. Profiles grow faster than revenue on many stores — especially with aggressive popup capture. Model 12-month profile growth before signing annual plans. Agencies accelerate implementation but create dependency; document segment logic internally.',
    'Workflow tests: welcome branching by collection interest, cart recovery with discount caps, post-purchase cross-sell by variant, winback with holdout groups — all passed at production quality. Klaviyo is the right default when data depth beats guidance speed.',
  ],
  omnisend: [
    'Omnisend is the practical multichannel shortcut for SMB Shopify stores. One-click install, prebuilt cart and welcome flows, and email + SMS + push in one builder got a home goods store from Shopify Email to full lifecycle in eleven days. Less flexible than Klaviyo for exotic data models, but faster for teams without a retention specialist.',
